'''Caius Faatili''' (born 9 November 2001) is a New Zealand  professional [[rugby league]] [[footballer]] who plays as a {{rlp|pr}} for [[Wakefield Trinity]] in the [[Super League]].

==Career==
===2025===
Faatili made his debut in round 1 of the [[2025 Super League season]] for Trinity against the [[Leeds Rhinos]].<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.superleague.co.uk/match-centre/report/43416 |title=Super League Match Report |publisher=Super League |date=15 February 2025}}</ref>

